      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a museum-quality E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of the S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit features a meticulously maintained high-pressure double VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, ensuring razor-sharp throttle response up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is structurally reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points, a critical preventative measure for this platform. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the M-Variable differential lock. With zero rod bearing wear and a pristine underside, this example represents a turnkey investment for the discerning enthusiast seeking mechanical purity.",
